PN,40301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FThe woman leading the investigation
OL,8,Finto maternity services in England
OL,9,Ffound the ceiling of an antenatal ward
OL,10,Fpropped up by metal poles when she
OL,11,Fvisited Taunton's Musgrove Park
OL,12,FHospital during her review.
OL,14,FConcerns over patient safety were also
OL,15,Fraised, with Baroness Amos describing
OL,16,F"significant emotional distress (among
OL,17,Fstaff), more than any other Trust we
OL,18,Fvisited".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FIn her report published today (June
OL,8,F30) the baroness described the
OL,9,FSomerset hospital as the "most
OL,10,Fchallenging" estate she visited during
OL,11,Fher investigation, describing it as "a
OL,12,Fpost-war building not designed for
OL,13,Fcurrent patient volumes or complexity
OL,14,Fof care".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FThe report says: "Many parts of the
OL,8,Festate at Musgrove Park are old and
OL,9,Fnot designed to deliver twenty-first
OL,10,Fcentury care. There were leaking
OL,11,Froofs, poor temperature control with
OL,12,Frooms often too hot or too cold, and
OL,13,Fthe ceiling of the antenatal ward was
OL,14,Fpropped up by metal poles."
OL,16,F"Staff described how two recovery
OL,17,Frooms on the labour ward could not be
OL,18,Fused during poor weather and had to be
OL,19,Ftaken out of use when it rained,
OL,20,Fincreasing pressure on accommodation
OL,21,Feven further."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FStaff reported concerns about heavy
OL,8,Fworkloads, staff shortages, along with
OL,9,Fracism and bullying. Baroness Amos
OL,10,Fsaid the emotional distress she
OL,11,Fencountered at Musgrove was "more than
OL,12,Fany other trust we visited".
OL,14,FShe wrote: "I find midwives in tears
OL,15,For support workers in tears because
OL,16,Fthey have not had a break, they have
OL,17,Fnot been able to go to the loo when
OL,18,Fthey needed to go."
OL,26,@vD@LOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FConcerns were also raised by the
OL,8,Finspection team about standards of
OL,9,Fcare at Yeovil District Hospital's
OL,10,Fmaternity unit which was shut when
OL,11,Fthey visited because of concerns about
OL,12,Fpatient safety.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FBaroness Amos said: "We have not
OL,8,Frevisited Yeovil District Hospital
OL,9,Fsince it opened. However, from the
OL,10,Fevidence we collected during our
OL,11,Fvisits and the concerns expressed by
OL,12,Fstaff, we remain concerned about
OL,13,Fpatient safety at Yeovil District
OL,14,FHospital. We are not convinced that
OL,15,Factions taken to address the CQC
OL,16,Fconcerns around insufficient
OL,17,Fpaediatric consultant staffing will
OL,18,Fprovide the necessary expertise to
OL,19,Fdelivery neonatal emergency cover."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FShe added: "We are troubled by the
OL,8,Ffact that a group of obstetric
OL,9,Fconsultants refused to provide
OL,10,Fservices at Musgrove Park Hospital
OL,11,Fduring Yeovil District Hospital's
OL,12,Fperiod of closure.
OL,14,F"We were not convinced by the
OL,15,Fexplanation that these staff
OL,16,Fmaintained clinical skills during the
OL,17,Fclosure of Yeovil District Hospital.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"We are also concerned about whether
OL,8,Fthe cultural problems that previously
OL,9,Fexisted have been resolved,
OL,10,Fparticularly given the disengagement
OL,11,Fof this group."
OL,13,FIn response to the report Dr Melanie
OL,14,FIles, Chief Medical Officer for
OL,15,FSomerset NHS Foundation Trust,
OL,16,Fapologised to anyone who had
OL,17,Fexperienced trauma or been let down.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FShe said: "Our teams have done a huge
OL,8,Famount of work to improve maternity
OL,9,Fand neonatal services and to provide
OL,10,Fsafe, compassionate care to the women,
OL,11,Fbabies, children and families we care
OL,12,Ffor ` but we have more work to do. We
OL,13,Fwill listen to our service users'
OL,14,Ffeedback, work with our independent
OL,15,FMaternity and Neonatal Voices
OL,16,FPartnership to ensure we fully
OL,17,Funderstand their experiences, and act
OL,18,Fon recommendations."
OL,26,@oD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FShe added: "Our local report
OL,8,Fhighlights the impact of the old,
OL,9,Foutdated and cramped maternity unit at
OL,10,FMusgrove Park Hospital on mothers,
OL,11,Fbabies, families and maternity
OL,12,Fcolleagues. We have made as many
OL,13,Fimprovements as possible to this
OL,14,Fbuilding, but it is not fit for use in
OL,15,Fa modern NHS and needs to be replaced
OL,16,Furgently.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"New women's and children's facilities
OL,8,Fare part of our New Hospitals
OL,9,FProgramme, but the start of
OL,10,Fconstruction has been delayed by the
OL,11,Fnational programme until 2033. We are
OL,12,Fexploring other possibilities, but the
OL,13,Fstate of our mothers and children's
OL,14,Ffacilities at Musgrove Park Hospital
OL,15,Fneeds to be urgently addressed
OL,17,FStaff under pressure, an ageing estate
OL,18,Fand concerns 'dismissed' in
OL,19,FGloucestershire
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FBaroness Amos also raised concerns
OL,8,Faround maternity care in
OL,9,FGloucestershire.
OL,11,FShe wrote: "During our investigation,
OL,12,Fwe spent two days at Gloucestershire,
OL,13,Fincluding a full walkaround of all
OL,14,Fareas where maternity and neonatal
OL,15,Fcare are delivered as well as visiting
OL,16,FStroud Maternity Unit."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FNHS-supported home birth services in
OL,8,FGloucestershire have been paused by
OL,9,Fthe Gloucestershire Hospitals NHS
OL,10,FFoundation Trust since November 2025
OL,11,Fdue to severe staffing shortages and
OL,12,Fsafety concerns.
OL,14,FShe added: "At the Gloucester site,
OL,15,Fthe layout of services allows for easy
OL,16,Fmobility between different areas,
OL,17,Fincluding the postnatal ward and
OL,18,Fneonatal services. However, staff
OL,19,Fconsistently reported that high levels
OL,20,Fof acuity were placing significant
OL,21,Fpressure on the service.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"Staff also highlighted limited
OL,8,Ftheatre capacity, which was not
OL,9,Fkeeping pace withthe rising number of
OL,10,Fcaesarean sections, leading to
OL,11,Fprocedures being cancelled or
OL,12,Frearranged.
OL,14,F"Concerns were also raised about
OL,15,Fbereavement facilities, where limited
OL,16,Fsoundproofing in delivery rooms
OL,17,Fincreased distress for families
OL,18,Fexperiencing loss."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FShe said staff described being under
OL,8,Fsustained pressure, "with demand and
OL,9,Fcomplexity increasing faster than
OL,10,Fstaffing, capacity and resources".
OL,12,F"Staff told us that the estate
OL,13,Faffected the safety, dignity and
OL,14,Fwellbeing of women, and their
OL,15,Fexperiences of care," she added.
OL,17,FBaroness Amos said that while
OL,18,Findividual staff members were
OL,19,Frecognised as kind and compassionate,
OL,20,Fsome families still felt like their
OL,21,Fconcerns were dismissed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FShe wrote: "Staffing levels are
OL,8,Fcausing risks to neonatal services
OL,9,Fwhere at times new admissions must be
OL,10,Fpaused.
OL,12,F"A lack of staffing is made worse by
OL,13,Ffinancial pressures across the Trust,
OL,14,Fwith managers interpreting costsaving
OL,15,Frestrictions to not allowing the
OL,16,Fbooking of bank staff and reported
OL,17,Fthat this limited their ability to
OL,18,Frespond to predictable surges in
OL,19,Fdemand, even where staff were
OL,20,Favailable and willing to take on
OL,21,Fadditional shifts.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"The services in the two sites across
OL,8,Fthe Trust are very different.
OL,10,F"The Gloucestershire Royal Hospital is
OL,11,Frunning with high demand and a service
OL,12,Fthat is stretched thin.
OL,14,F"Stroud has low birth numbers but
OL,15,Foffers personalised care in a quiet
OL,16,Fsetting.
OL,18,F"Home births are paused, and the
OL,19,Ffreestanding maternity unit in
OL,20,FCheltenham is closed for births due to
OL,21,Fstaffing and safety concerns.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40318
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"This seriously restricts choice of
OL,8,Fplanned place of birth for women and
OL,9,Ffurther increases pressure on services
OL,10,Fat Gloucestershire Royal Hospital.
OL,12,F"The executive team are aware of the
OL,13,Fchallenges regarding the inconsistency
OL,14,Fof care, the pressure staff are
OL,15,Fworking under, and the staffing and
OL,16,Ffinancial pressures.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40319
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"Whilst mitigations and action plans,
OL,8,Fsuch as cultural improvement plans and
OL,9,Frecruitment measures are in place,
OL,10,Fthere needs to be a large-scale shift
OL,11,Fin efforts to address these
OL,12,Fchallenges, together with investment
OL,13,Fin community and hospital-based
OL,14,Fservices.
OL,16,F"Women need to be listened to,
OL,17,Finvolved in decisions about their care
OL,18,Fand treated with compassion."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G19/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40320
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FIn a statement the Gloucestershire
OL,8,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust said:
OL,9,F"We are deeply sorry to the women,
OL,10,Fbabies, families and our staff whose
OL,11,Fexperiences of our maternity and
OL,12,Fneonatal services did not meet the
OL,13,Fstandards they have the right to
OL,14,Fexpect. We recognise the lasting
OL,15,Fimpact this has had.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G20/21
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40321
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782839906
OL,3,CTearful staff raised concerns about
OL,4,Cpatient care in national maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"We are also deeply concerned by the
OL,8,Faccounts of discrimination and wider
OL,9,Fsocial inequalities experienced within
OL,10,Fmaternity services. We know there is
OL,11,Fmore to do, and we are committed to
OL,12,Fimproving the consistency, safety and
OL,13,Fquality of care for every family."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G21/21
